race.comment: TROPHY DARTS (8) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 19.50 beating Phoenix Amelia. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. In sparkling form and expected to measure up again. RED EMPEROR (5) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 0.8 lengths (30.90) at this track. Can measure up again. BUFFY'S NO ANGEL (2) flew the lids and led throughout to score last time at big odds, winning by 3.5 lengths at this track over 595m (34.74). Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Should be in this for a long way. NOD FEENY (1) has not raced over this journey but still warrants respect.
